==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Grater
<hw>Grat"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From Qrate, v.]</ety>
<def>One who, or that which, grates; especially, an instrument or
utensil with a rough, indented surface, for rubbing off small particles
of any substance; <as>as a <ex>grater</ex> for nutmegs</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Graticulation</ent>⟦br⟧
